spec_data.Name: perl-Web-Scraper
spec_data.Description:
Web::Scraper is a web scraper toolkit, inspired by Ruby's equivalent
Scrapi. It provides a DSL-ish interface for traversing HTML documents and
returning a neatly arranged Perl data structure.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 06:22:00 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Web Scraping Toolkit using HTML and CSS Selectors or XPath expressions
